## Quick Pre-Commit Command

```bash
export PATH="/home/ubuntu/.local/bin:$PATH" && pre-commit run --all-files
```

## Project Standards

- **Formatting**: Black with line-length=100
- **Import sorting**: isort with --profile=black
- **Comments**: Use AICODE-NOTE, AICODE-TODO, AICODE-ASK
- **Testing**: Always update/add tests for code changes
- **Documentation**: Update docs_site/ after new features
- **Pre-commit**: ALWAYS run before committing - NO EXCEPTIONS

